FORMER Speaker of Parliament Speaker and PF Zapu stalwart Cyril Ndebele has died. By Linda ChinobvaFORMER Speaker of Parliament Speaker and PF Zapu stalwart Cyril NdebeleNdebele passed on in the morning in Bulawayo but the cause of his death is yet to be established.Zapu deputy national spokesperson Iphithule Maphosa confirmed Ndebele s death.Ndebele became Parliament Speaker in 1995. He fell out of favour with President Robert Mugabe when he issued a parliamentary certificate advising Zanu PF that it should not discipline then ruling party Masvingo chairman, Dzikamai Mavhaire for asking Mugabe to step down.More details to follow